ard Latin Pop Airplay\"]</ref>\n| align=\"center\" | 6\n| align=\"center\" | 1\n|-\n| align=\"left\" | \"[[Quiero Estar Contigo (Alejandra Guzm\u00e1n song)|Quiero Estar Contigo]]\"<ref>[http://www.billboard.com/charts/2006-11-25/latin-pop-songs \"Quiero Estar Contigo: Billboard Latin Pop Airplay\"]</ref>\n| align=\"center\" | -\n| align=\"center\" | 27\n|-\n| align=\"center\" rowspan=\"2\" | 2007\n| align=\"left\" | \"[[Soy S\u00f3lo Un Secreto]]\"<ref>[http://www.billboard.com/charts/2008-04-05/latin-pop-songs \"Soy S\u00f3lo Un Secreto: Billboard Latin Pop Airplay\"]</ref>\n| align=\"center\" | 12\n| align=\"center\" | 3\n|-\n| align=\"left\" | \"M\u00edrame\"\n| align=\"center\" | -\n| align=\"center\" | -\n|-\n| align=\"center\" rowspan=\"1\" | 2010\n| align=\"left\" | \"[[Que Cante la Vida (charity single)|Que Cante la Vida]]\"\n| align=\"center\" | -\n| align=\"center\" | -\n|-\n| align=\"center\" rowspan=\"2\" | 2011\n| align=\"left\" | \"[[Tan S\u00f3lo T\u00fa]]\" <small>([[Franco De Vita]] featuring Alejandra Guzm\u00e1n)</small>\n| align=\"center\" | 14\n| align=\"center\" | 3\n|-\n| align=\"left\" | \"[[D\u00eda de Suerte]]\"\n| align=\"center\" | 9\n| align=\"center\" | 2\n|-\n|- bgcolor=\"#CCCCCC\"\n| align=\"center\" colspan=\"2\" | '''Total number-one hits\n| align=\"center\" | -\n| align=\"center\" | 1\n|}\n\n== Tours ==\n[[File:Alejandra_Guzm\u00e1n_at_Denver_Coliseum_2.jpg|thumb|right|250px|Alejandra Guzm\u00e1n at Denver Coliseum, 2009.]]\n* Dame Tu Amor Tour (1990)\n* Eternamente Bella Tour (1991)\n* Flor de Papel Tour (1992)\n* Libre Tour (1993\u201394)\n* Enorme Tour (1995\u201396)\n* Cambio de Piel Tour (1997)\n* La Guzman Tour (1998)\n* Algo Natural Tour (1999-2000)\n* Soy Tour (2002)\n* Supersexitada Tour (2004\u201305)\n* Indeble (2006\u201307)\n* Fuerza Tour (2008\u201309)\n* Unico Tour (2010)\n* 20 A\u00f1os de \u00c9xitos Tour (2011\u201312)\n* La Guzman Primera Fila Tour (2014)\n* Rock Recargado Tour (2015)\n* A + No Poder Tour (2016)